<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../646/64646.xml">
Toronto</link></village>
, Robert first became interested and involved in the Olympic Bid process during the 1996 <event wordnetid="100029378" confidence="0.8">
<social_event wordnetid="107288639" confidence="0.8">
<contest wordnetid="107456188" confidence="0.8">
