<p>

Also an author, Robert Livingstone has contributed editorial content for newspapers and magazines including a series about New York's 2012 Olympic bid in the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../625/49625.xml">
New York Sun</link> newspaper<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%225%22])">5</ref>. </p>
<p>

Livingstone has provided consultative guidance for bid committees and enjoys meeting with bid team members to learn about their campaigns. He also makes personal appearances with various social and business groups to discuss the impact of the Olympic bid process and the Olympic Games. </p>
